---
---
<section id="process" class="py-16 bg-white border-b border-slate-200">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 mb-3">
        <span class="w-8 h-0.5 bg-accent"></span>
        <span class="text-xs font-condensed font-extrabold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500">ENGINEERING CYCLE</span>
        <span class="w-8 h-0.5 bg-accent"></span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-condensed font-bold text-brand-navy uppercase tracking-tight">
        Our Structured Detailing Process
      </h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mt-3 font-sans max-w-xl mx-auto">
        A disciplined, 5-stage workflow focused on minimizing RFIs and ensuring schedule reliability.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Linear Step Layout (Horizontal on LG, Vertical below) -->
    <div class="relative">
      
      <!-- Connecting Line for Desktop (hidden on mobile) -->
      <div class="absolute top-[48px] left-[5%] right-[5%] h-1 bg-slate-200 hidden lg:block z-0"></div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-8 relative z-10">
        
        <!-- Step 1: Discovery -->
        <div class="flex flex-col bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-6 rounded-none relative">
          <!-- Step indicator bullet -->
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-navy text-white text-sm font-condensed font-bold flex items-center justify-center mb-4 border-2 border-accent mx-auto lg:mx-0">
            01
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-condensed font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-brand-navy text-center lg:text-left">
            Discovery & Intake
          </h3>
          <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 font-sans mt-2 leading-relaxed text-center lg:text-left">
            Establish project scope. Review structural & architectural drawings, define fabricator specific standards, and lock in milestone schedules.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-sans mt-4 space-y-1 border-t border-slate-200 pt-3 hidden sm:block">
            <li>• RFQ / Contract alignment</li>
            <li>• Standard Setup (AS 4100)</li>
            <li>• Project timeline definition</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2: Modelling -->
        <div class="flex flex-col bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-6 rounded-none relative">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-navy text-white text-sm font-condensed font-bold flex items-center justify-center mb-4 border-2 border-accent mx-auto lg:mx-0">
            02
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-condensed font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-brand-navy text-center lg:text-left">
            3D BIM Modelling
          </h3>
          <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 font-sans mt-2 leading-relaxed text-center lg:text-left">
            Build the parametric structural model in Tekla. Coordinate connections, perform internal clash-detection, and flag RFI questions.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-sans mt-4 space-y-1 border-t border-slate-200 pt-3 hidden sm:block">
            <li>• Tekla Structures model entry</li>
            <li>• Connection engineering checks</li>
            <li>• RFI generation & submission</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3: Detailing -->
        <div class="flex flex-col bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-6 rounded-none relative">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-navy text-white text-sm font-condensed font-bold flex items-center justify-center mb-4 border-2 border-accent mx-auto lg:mx-0">
            03
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-condensed font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-brand-navy text-center lg:text-left">
            Detailing & Extraction
          </h3>
          <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 font-sans mt-2 leading-relaxed text-center lg:text-left">
            Extract precise shop drawings from the approved 3D model. Develop general arrangements, assemblies, and single-part drawings.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-sans mt-4 space-y-1 border-t border-slate-200 pt-3 hidden sm:block">
            <li>• GA drawing layouts</li>
            <li>• Part and Assembly extraction</li>
            <li>• Bolt & hardware schedules</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4: Review -->
        <div class="flex flex-col bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-6 rounded-none relative">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-navy text-white text-sm font-condensed font-bold flex items-center justify-center mb-4 border-2 border-accent mx-auto lg:mx-0">
            04
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-condensed font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-brand-navy text-center lg:text-left">
            Quality QA & Checking
          </h3>
          <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 font-sans mt-2 leading-relaxed text-center lg:text-left">
            Dedicated senior checkers review drawings against design layouts. Verify members, fits, erection clearances, and standard compliance.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-sans mt-4 space-y-1 border-t border-slate-200 pt-3 hidden sm:block">
            <li>• Multi-level checklist review</li>
            <li>• RFI resolution check</li>
            <li>• Pre-issue authorization</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 5: Delivery -->
        <div class="flex flex-col bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-6 rounded-none relative">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-navy text-white text-sm font-condensed font-bold flex items-center justify-center mb-4 border-2 border-accent mx-auto lg:mx-0">
            05
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-condensed font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-brand-navy text-center lg:text-left">
            Fabrication Delivery
          </h3>
          <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 font-sans mt-2 leading-relaxed text-center lg:text-left">
            Export and compile final deliverables. Issue standard drawings alongside production files (NC, KISS) for automated fabrication machinery.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-sans mt-4 space-y-1 border-t border-slate-200 pt-3 hidden sm:block">
            <li>• PDF and DWG drawing release</li>
            <li>• NC1 & KISS files delivery</li>
            <li>• Ongoing fabrication support</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
